[size=4][b]Hytale Auto-Repair Mod
[/b][/size]
[size=2]Using this mod, you can prevent tools from breaking by automatically using repair kits from your inventory.
[/size]
[size=3][b]Base Features
[/b]
[/size][list]
[*][size=2]Â `/autorepair` command to toggle the auto-repair feature[/size]
[*]if the auto-repair feature is enabled and a tool in your inventory breaks, it will automatically be repaired as long as you have a repair kit in your inventory
[*]You get a chat message when an item is auto-repaired
[*]The `/autorepair` state (enabled/disabled) will be persisted, so that leaving a server and re-joining keeps the last setting
[/list]
[size=3][b]How to Download

[/b][/size][size=2]The mod can be downloaded from [Curseforge](https://www.curseforge.com/hytale/mods/auto-repair) or [Nexusmods](https://www.nexusmods.com/hytale/mods/42).[/size]
[size=2]Just add the `.jar` to your server's mods folder (or directly install on your server using the Curseforge UI).[/size]
[size=2]
After installing the mod, you can execute the `/autorepair` command in your in-game chat.[/size]
[size=2]You can always toggle this mod on and off by executing `/autorepair` again.

[/size]
